org.apache.commons.io.function

Interface IOSpliterator<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of elements returned by this IOSpliterator.

    public interface IOSpliterator<T>
    Like Spliterator but throws IOException.
    Since:
    2.12.0
